where you had to take decisions

00:34:16.020 --> 00:34:19.698
consciously to help
you break through?

00:34:19.698 --> 00:34:21.739
OBY ESEKWESILI: You see,
one of the things that I

00:34:21.739 --> 00:34:24.000
loved about what
Ibukun was saying

00:34:24.000 --> 00:34:25.864
