00:34:27.739 --> 00:34:30.050
But I think I heard
that word, contextual.

00:34:30.050 --> 00:34:31.760
Context is so important.

00:34:31.760 --> 00:34:35.800
And in policy school, I was
taught that without context,

00:34:35.800 --> 00:34:37.010
you run into trouble.

00:34:37.010 --> 00:34:40.350
The reason I say this is
that there are some women,

00:34:40.350 --> 00:34:47.860
