managed to not see this glass,

00:34:47.860 --> 00:34:49.070
even when it was--

00:34:49.070 --> 00:34:49.570
[LAUGHTER]

00:34:49.570 --> 00:34:50.520
JULIET EHUMIAN-CHIAZOR:
Right there.

00:34:50.520 --> 00:34:52.936
OBY ESEKWESILI: I don't know
