ceiling conversation

00:35:44.140 --> 00:35:51.300
is actually the glass ceiling
that the individual places

00:35:51.300 --> 00:35:53.740
on themselves.

00:35:53.740 --> 00:35:54.380
OK?

00:35:54.380 --> 00:35:55.588
JULIET EHUMIAN-CHIAZOR: Yeah.

00:35:55.588 --> 00:35:58.732
OBY ESEKWESILI: So if there
