that's a glass ceiling.

00:35:59.690 --> 00:36:00.898
JULIET EHUMIAN-CHIAZOR: Yeah.

00:36:00.898 --> 00:36:03.330
OBY ESEKWESILI: When
a woman sort of says

00:36:03.330 --> 00:36:06.750
to herself, every time that
