00:44:09.920 --> 00:44:13.250
And certainly, our
hearts and prayers

00:44:13.250 --> 00:44:16.450
go to the girls
and their families.

00:44:16.450 --> 00:44:22.020
Do you feel gender has
played a role at all?

00:44:22.020 --> 00:44:25.856
Do you feel equally supported
by men in this campaign?

00:44:25.856 --> 00:44:34.340
OBY ESEKWESILI: Oh, actually, a
lot of the people who came out

00:44:34.340 --> 00:44:41.000
on the 13th of April, when we
